videos.headline: Shepard puts Oklahoma on the board
videos.description: Baker Mayfield throws to Sterling Shepard for the 4-yard touchdown to put Oklahoma up 7-3.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State retakes the lead
videos.description: J.W. Walsh's pass is complete to Jhajuan Seales for the 26-yard touchdown to put Oklahoma State back up 10-7.

videos.headline: Devante Averette lays a huge hit on Alex Ross
videos.description: During an Oklahoma kickoff return, Oklahoma State's Devante Averette lays a huge hit on Alex Ross.

videos.headline: Samaje Perine takes it to the house
videos.description: Oklahoma running back Samaje Perine gets the handoff and rushes 68 yards for the touchdown to put Oklahoma up 14-10 over Oklahoma State.

videos.headline: Mixon turns direction and scores
videos.description: Oklahoma RB Joe Mixon initially runs to the left but is shut down, so he reverses course into the open field and scores a 66-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Sooners extend lead with pick-six
